            "text": "<p>Discover the Phoenix range at Cook & Bathe, including premium tapware, showers, and bathroom accessories designed for Australian kitchens and bathrooms. As a leader in innovative and stylish tapware, Phoenix products offer quality and water efficiency to elevate your renovation or new build.</p>"
