            "heading": "Phoenix Tapware for Your Home",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_XWFjiJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Phoenix is a leading Australian brand known for its award-winning tapware, showers, and bathroom accessories that combine timeless design with everyday practicality. With a commitment to excellence and innovation, Phoenix creates products that enhance kitchens, bathrooms, and laundries with elegant forms, superior functionality, and durable craftsmanship.</p><p>Whether you’re seeking a statement kitchen mixer, a luxurious shower experience, or refined bathroom tapware, Phoenix offers a diverse range of finishes and styles to suit modern Australian homes. Their products are designed with water efficiency and sustainability in mind, helping you create beautiful spaces that are also environmentally responsible.</p><p>At Cook & Bathe, we are proud to offer a curated selection of Phoenix’s best-selling and most popular products, ensuring our customers have access to premium tapware and accessories for their renovation or new build. Explore the Phoenix collection online or visit our Melbourne showrooms to experience the quality and design that Phoenix brings to your home.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
