    "multicolumn_DmjYfM": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_dpQBDC": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/139-7900-12-1_lifestyle1.webp",
            "title": "Tapware",
            "text": "<p>Discover Phoenix Tapware, a leader in premium kitchen and bathroom tapware designed for modern Australian homes. Phoenix tapware blends contemporary style with everyday practicality, offering a range of kitchen mixers and bathroom basin taps that elevate your renovation or new build. Known for water efficiency and durable finishes, Phoenix tapware delivers the quality and reliability homeowners and designers trust. Whether you’re updating your kitchen with a sleek mixer or enhancing your bathroom with a refined basin tap, Phoenix provides stylish solutions that enhance functionality while adding timeless appeal to your space. At Cook & Bathe, we proudly stock Phoenix’s best-selling tapware collections, making it easy to find the perfect tapware to suit your design vision. Explore Phoenix Tapware today to bring elegance and performance to your kitchen and bathroom.</p>",
            "link_label": "Phoenix Tapware",
            "link": "shopify://collections/phoenix-bathroom-tapware"
          }
        },
        "column_btBdt3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/119-0600-10_lifestyle.webp",
            "title": "Showers",
            "text": "<p>Experience the quality and design of Phoenix Showers, crafted to elevate your bathroom with style and performance. Phoenix offers a premium range of showers, including overhead, rail, and hand showers, designed for modern Australian bathrooms. Known for their innovative engineering and water-efficient technology, Phoenix showers deliver a luxurious shower experience while helping you save water. Whether you’re renovating your ensuite or upgrading your family bathroom, Phoenix showers combine sleek aesthetics with reliable functionality, making them a trusted choice for homeowners and designers alike. At Cook & Bathe, we stock a curated selection of Phoenix’s best-selling showers to help you create a bathroom that is both practical and beautiful. Explore Phoenix Showers today to transform your bathroom with elegant design and exceptional performance.</p>",
            "link_label": "Phoenix Showers",
            "link": "shopify://collections/phoenix-showers"
          }
        },
        "column_JE3UyW": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/300-2111-50_Lifestyle.webp",
            "title": "Sinks",
            "text": "<p>Discover the elegance and practicality of Phoenix sinks, designed to elevate your kitchen and laundry spaces with modern Australian style. Phoenix offers a range of premium sinks crafted with durable materials and sleek finishes that seamlessly blend with contemporary interiors. Whether you’re renovating your kitchen or updating your laundry, Phoenix sinks provide practical solutions with generous bowl sizes and functional designs that enhance your daily routine. Known for quality craftsmanship and timeless aesthetics, Phoenix sinks are a trusted choice for homeowners and designers seeking to add sophistication and functionality to their projects. At Cook & Bathe, we proudly offer a curated selection of Phoenix sinks, making it easy to find the perfect addition to your renovation or new build. Explore Phoenix sinks today and transform your space with quality and style.</p>",
            "link_label": "Phoenix Sinks",
            "link": "shopify://collections/phoenix-sinks"
          }
        },
        "column_M8YzXf": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/134-1070-40_Lifestyle1.webp",
            "title": "Accessories",
            "text": "<p>Enhance your kitchen and bathroom with Phoenix accessories, designed to complement modern Australian homes with style and practicality. Phoenix offers a premium range of bathroom accessories, including towel rails, soap dishes, robe hooks, and toilet roll holders, as well as functional kitchen accessories that add convenience to your daily routine. Known for their sleek designs and quality finishes, Phoenix accessories bring a cohesive look to your renovation or new build while ensuring everyday functionality. Whether you are updating your bathroom or completing your kitchen space, Phoenix accessories deliver the perfect blend of elegance and durability. At Cook & Bathe, we proudly stock a curated selection of Phoenix’s best-selling accessories, making it easy to find the right finishing touches for your home. Explore Phoenix accessories today and elevate your kitchen and bathroom with practical, stylish solutions.</p>",
            "link_label": "Phoenix Accessories",
            "link": "shopify://collections/phoenix-bathroom-accessories"
          }
        }
      },
